[Student "S"]
{With 18 points you have enough to make a Reverse. So you bid 2\D. Partner now says 3\S.  

Partner's jump bid shows a 6-card suit and enough points to insist on game. You don't have \S support but you do have good \H stoppers so you bid 3NT.}

